Global Industrial Screw Vacuum Pumps Market Insights
Industrial Screw Vacuum Pumps Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Industrial Screw Vacuum Pumps Market Overview
The global Industrial Screw Vacuum Pumps market is estimated to reach a value of approximately USD 3.4 billion by 2028, growing at a robust CAGR of around 5.2% from 2021 to 2028. This growth can be attributed to the increasing demand for energy-efficient, high-performance vacuum pumps across various industrial applications, including manufacturing, food processing, and chemical industries. The rapid advancements in technology and rising focus on sustainable and environmentally friendly practices further enhance the market potential. Industrial screw vacuum pumps, known for their high efficiency and low maintenance, are becoming an integral part of industrial applications, leading to a surge in market value.

